By the definition of `Nat.recAux`, this is `(fun m ih => Vector.push < > ih < > OracelComp.uniformSample α inst) (m) (Nat.recAux (pure #v[]) (fun m ih => Vector.push < > ih < > OracelComp.uniformSample α inst) m)`.
So we need to show `x ∈ support ((fun m ih => Vector.push < > ih < > OracelComp.uniformSample α inst) (m) (Nat.recAux (pure #v[]) (fun m ih => Vector.push < > ih < > OracelComp.uniformSample α inst) m))`.
