Also, `x.head ∈ α`, and `α` is `SampleableType` (from `hα`), so `x.head` is in the support of `uniformSample α`, meaning `Pr[= x.head | $ᵗ α] > 0`.
Therefore, their product is positive.
This shows `x ∈ support (Rec_{m+1})`.

